Mix peanut butter, chocolate chips, golden raisins, raisins, honey, cinnamon, nutmeg, and allspice together in a bowl; mix in hemp seeds until mixture is firm and the consistency of cookie dough. Spread chia seeds onto a plate. Coat hands with canola oil and roll peanut butter mixture into balls. Roll balls in the chia seeds until coated. Chill energy chunks in refrigerator until solid, about 1 hour.